pullrequest.title: Turn on gravity for sensors and give them collision shapes.

content.raw: I wouldn't bother trying to sync up old versions of model.sdf. The plan is to deprecrate them following the next release. This will be the point at  which sdf version 1.3 has been out for over 2 release cycles.
